Incumbents[edit]

  • President – Heinrich Lübke
  • Chancellor – Ludwig Erhard (until 30 November), Kurt Georg Kiesinger (starting 30 November)

Events[edit]

  • Germany in the Eurovision Song Contest 1966
  • June 24 - July 5 - 16th Berlin International Film Festival
  • December 1 - The Kiesinger cabinet led by Kurt Georg Kiesinger was sworn in.
  • Date unknown: German company Hannover Re was founded.
